估到係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nGogogo <br />\n<br />\n人血九大鬼正冚家剷，唔爭在順手加埋燒山呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T18:38:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T18:49:39.000Z","msg":"Nonono <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n燒山咁義正辭嚴反對接受委任<br />\n<br />\n係對而家嘅接受委任既泛民主派一個衝擊<br />\n<br />\n唔好唔記得燒山好多人睇，係有一定程度嘅煽動力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁做客觀效果無疑會令民主陣營內部出現爭拗，產生內訌<br />\n<br />\n足以破壞泛民統一，已經構成「分裂泛民罪」，可以正式宣佈燒山納入人血九大鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n燒山同毓民以前一齊組過政黨，之後嘅決裂好明顯係做假<br />\n<br />\n一個黑面，一個白面，中間一定打晒籠統<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n燒山肯定收咗毓民錢搞分化，從呢一點已經可以斷定燒山<br />\n<br />\n係PR下既「毓線」人物<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48147fad433f7f6748d8e2f2d96e06c2cbc33a60","tid":2163602,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T18:50:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b34911b7fbba3340b08b28b3f302020308246195","tid":2163602,"uid":143499,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T18:50:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b2e3e28ae91175a39875013f3af3a3a2edf7c023","tid":2163602,"uid":219007,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b6901ec91562bbb67846904fcf1b685568ca7eb3","tid":2163602